_Unification/working/codex-run-v2.log:1320:_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/CRM.md:319:RFP tracking occurs in Monday\.com, creating duplicate entry and preventing unified pipeline reporting\. Leadership lacks visibility into RFP workload and win/loss performance alongside standard opportunities\. 
_Unification/working/codex-run-v2.log:1321:_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/CRM.md:363:Currently, HubSpot does not capture GP\. Only the deal amount is entered at the opportunity stage\. No gross profit fields or margin calculations are being tracked within HubSpot today\.
