_Unification/working/codex-run-v2.log:1325:_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/CRM.md:415:Leadership views dashboards scoped to their teams\. Sales operations updates the hierarchy in NetSuite Orion, and reports adjust automatically\. Territory\-based reporting ensures SVPs and reps see relevant data in real time\. 
_Unification/working/codex-run-v2.log:1326:_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/CRM.md:449:Annual goals live in HubSpot, while the 2\.5× multiplier is calculated manually in 15:5 reviews and PowerBI\. Reps lack real\-time visibility into multiplier status\. 
_Unification/working/codex-run-v2.log:1327:_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/CRM.md:491:Activity logging in HubSpot is enforced manually for new hires and underperformers\. Experienced reps have flexibility, and there is limited visibility into coaching effectiveness\. 
