_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/CRM.md:137:NetSuite Orion is an industry\-specific configuration of NetSuite tailored for contract furniture dealers\. It unifies CRM, quoting, project execution, procurement, and financial management on a single cloud platform\. CRM capabilities include opportunity management with custom stages and probabilities, multi\-company relationship tracking, activity and task management, goal tracking, and robust analytics\. Native integration with NetSuite ERP ensures that quote, order, and invoice data feed directly back into CRM dashboards for real\-time visibility\. NetSuite Orion's workflow engine and saved search analytics enable low\-code automation and executive\-ready reporting without extensive customization\.
