"You can just take a screenshot of that for us too.","startTime":"12:32","endTime":"12:35","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Definitely.","startTime":"12:36","endTime":"12:36","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yep.","startTime":"12:36","endTime":"12:37","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"Yeah, let's do that.","startTime":"12:38","endTime":"12:38","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"That way we don't have to ask you again because we'll get in the meeting, we'll be talking about it.","startTime":"12:38","endTime":"12:43","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We're like, what was that again?","startTime":"12:43","endTime":"12:44","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Yeah, if you have any documentation, that'll help.","startTime":"12:45","endTime":"12:47","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I do.","startTime":"12:48","endTime":"12:48","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yep.","startTime":"12:48","endTime":"12:49","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Perfect.","startTime":"12:49","endTime":"12:49","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Thank you.","startTime":"12:49","endTime":"12:50","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So for the sake of the transcript.","startTime":"12:51","endTime":"12:52","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Kip will be sending that to us as well.","startTime":"12:52","endTime":"12:54","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"And then do you have some type of workflow for accepting those quotes from vendors?","startTime":"12:57","endTime":"13:07","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Like official acceptance and rejection?","startTime":"13:09","endTime":"13:11","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Is that just.","startTime":"13:12","endTime":"13:13","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"You either get a PO or you don't get a po.","startTime":"13:13","endTime":"13:15","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"That's our official.","startTime":"13:15","endTime":"13:16","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"13:18","endTime":"13:18","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"No email communication or anything like that.","startTime":"13:20","endTime":"13:22","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I mean, sometimes there's an email communication if the PM or the AM decides to.","startTime":"13:22","endTime":"13:29","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"But usually, you know, we put their quote number on the line and we issue a PO against that line, and our PO references their quote number, and that's our acceptance of their quote.","startTime":"13:29","endTime":"13:40","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Great.","startTime":"13:41","endTime":"13:41","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And when you're doing the labor quote.","startTime":"13:43","endTime":"13:46","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"You don't have your quote in the system.","startTime":"13:47","endTime":"13:48","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Well, you're building it probably in spec, right?","startTime":"13:49","endTime":"13:51","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Depends.","startTime":"13:52","endTime":"13:53","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Sometimes we're building it in spec, sometimes we're building it in core.","startTime":"13:53","endTime":"13:55","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"13:55","endTime":"13:56","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"When you, so you do your, you get the labor quote back and then you either going to bring that over in the sift file or you're going to put the lines on inside of core and you'll do the same thing in Orion.","startTime":"13:57","endTime":"14:10","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So we have a process in Orion where you can accept a specific labor quote and then you can also then decide what information from that labor quote wants to come over.","startTime":"14:12","endTime":"14:20","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So and when we get the configuration, this will make a bit more sense because we'll kind of, we'll build it out that form.","startTime":"14:20","endTime":"14:27","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We'll use what you're working as a template.","startTime":"14:27","endTime":"14:29","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But typically do you bring it over as one total line or do you itemize it?","startTime":"14:29","endTime":"14:34","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I shouldn't say typically.","startTime":"14:34","endTime":"14:35","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Oftentimes it's one labor line, but sometimes we itemize it depending on the scope of the work.","startTime":"14:36","endTime":"14:41","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So if it's multi phase or we've asked for like four trip charges, but we're only going to issue a PO for one trip charge and hold back the three.","startTime":"14:41","endTime":"14:50","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So there's a lot of different stuff.","startTime":"14:50","endTime":"14:52","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Kimmy can speak in more depth about kind of the ways that AMs play around with that.","startTime":"14:52","endTime":"14:57","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"You said it pretty well.","startTime":"15:00","endTime":"15:01","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"I was to say that we anticipate erosion potential through drip charges and or sometimes hold a contingency that doesn't get released.","startTime":"15:01","endTime":"15:12","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"So we will add lines that are part of a grouped labor cell line and only issue the PoS related to the quoted cost that we are accepting.","startTime":"15:12","endTime":"15:26","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"15:27","endTime":"15:28","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"So we might ask them to over quote, but then we'll under issue the po hoping that we don't have to use the difference.","startTime":"15:29","endTime":"15:36","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"And if we do have to use the difference, it's in there.","startTime":"15:36","endTime":"15:38","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"And then we'll issue the PO as it's requested.","startTime":"15:38","endTime":"15:40","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"But.","startTime":"15:40","endTime":"15:40","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, but we're hoping.","startTime":"15:42","endTime":"15:45","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"To hold on to that money.","startTime":"15:45","endTime":"15:46","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"We GSI build a client, right.","startTime":"15:46","endTime":"15:49","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"If we do a good job, we take what we kept as our reward.","startTime":"15:49","endTime":"15:52","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So sure, yeah.","startTime":"15:52","endTime":"15:54","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Got it.","startTime":"15:54","endTime":"15:54","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And then going back, I do like.","startTime":"15:56","endTime":"15:59","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"The idea of being able to though.","startTime":"15:59","endTime":"16:00","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Like if a labor quote comes in, if we send out a labor quote request, it comes back in and then we can.","startTime":"16:00","endTime":"16:05","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Where we spend a lot of time is copying and pasting.","startTime":"16:06","endTime":"16:08","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So like the less copy and pasting we can do to get it to what it needs to be.","startTime":"16:08","endTime":"16:12","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"You know, there's a method that Orion has built in to do that, then we definitely want to look at what that process change could be.","startTime":"16:13","endTime":"16:22","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yep.","startTime":"16:22","endTime":"16:23","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yeah, definitely.","startTime":"16:23","endTime":"16:24","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"There's a labor quote acceptance feature and there's like a little modal that says, okay, I'm going to accept this labor quote and I'm going to decide what lines I want to have pass over to the quote, record either summary or itemized.","startTime":"16:24","endTime":"16:38","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And you can kind of.","startTime":"16:38","endTime":"16:39","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"You can kind of fiddle with that a little bit.","startTime":"16:39","endTime":"16:41","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And then it connects the quote and the labor quote together and it makes labor quote part of the project.","startTime":"16:41","endTime":"16:46","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So when we're doing all our project reporting later on, you have visibility starting at the labor quote, to the quote, to the sales order, to the invoice.","startTime":"16:46","endTime":"16:56","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And you know exactly yet you see all those costs and even purchase orders and bills.","startTime":"16:56","endTime":"17:01","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So you can have that visibility.","startTime":"17:02","endTime":"17:04","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And I'm thinking also, since you are, it's decentralized as far as who can send this out for quote.","startTime":"17:06","endTime":"17:11","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I imagine as far as accepting it is also decentralized.","startTime":"17:11","endTime":"17:15","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"There's not any specific person that could do the acceptance.","startTime":"17:15","endTime":"17:18","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It's really whoever's managing that.","startTime":"17:18","endTime":"17:20","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I'm assuming there's not like a rubber stamp by any means.","startTime":"17:20","endTime":"17:25","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Usually it's the account manager or the salesperson that's going to accept the final labor number or the PM if they get some help.","startTime":"17:25","endTime":"17:34","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Marcus, last month I requested like 50 labor quotes.","startTime":"17:34","endTime":"17:37","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So it's like anybody is available.","startTime":"17:37","endTime":"17:38","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"If you're willing and know how to, you can request a labor quote.","startTime":"17:39","endTime":"17:42","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Oftentimes what PMs are doing is they're presenting what they think we should do.","startTime":"17:43","endTime":"17:48","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So they might go get three quotes and then they make a recommendation.","startTime":"17:48","endTime":"17:51","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"But ultimately it's the sales side that makes the final decision on what labor we're going to use.","startTime":"17:52","endTime":"17:57","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"17:58","endTime":"17:58","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"17:58","endTime":"17:59","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"So this is a little bit different than some of the other dealers we work with.","startTime":"18:00","endTime":"18:02","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"With other dealers.","startTime":"18:02","endTime":"18:03","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It's a bit more centralized with some other dealers.","startTime":"18:03","endTime":"18:06","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"That's why I'm asking some of these clarifying questions.","startTime":"18:07","endTime":"18:09","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I just want to make sure that our team has a clear understanding on how you guys are working.","startTime":"18:09","endTime":"18:13","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And I could see the benefit of multiple people being able to do this because it's not bottlenecked through one person or two people.","startTime":"18:13","endTime":"18:20","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Yeah, well, we have so many different markets and market requirements.","startTime":"18:21","endTime":"18:25","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Kimmy, you have a thought?","startTime":"18:25","endTime":"18:27","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"What are you thinking?","startTime":"18:27","endTime":"18:28","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Well, I was.","startTime":"18:28","endTime":"18:29","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"I was going to ask a clarification question about something Marcus said that I didn't fully understand about.","startTime":"18:30","endTime":"18:36","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"You mentioned something about the labor quote and tying it to the order.","startTime":"18:37","endTime":"18:42","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Like, wouldn't.","startTime":"18:43","endTime":"18:44","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"It does it like live freely without association to quote until you tie it.","startTime":"18:44","endTime":"18:50","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"I guess I just don't understand that portion of it.","startTime":"18:50","endTime":"18:54","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"18:54","endTime":"18:55","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So the idea here is.","startTime":"18:55","endTime":"18:56","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"18:56","endTime":"18:56","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"The labor quote is this standalone record, and you could have multiple labor quotes because you may have sent multiple out, got multiple back, and now you got to choose which one.","startTime":"18:56","endTime":"19:07","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Sorry.","startTime":"19:08","endTime":"19:09","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"I see.","startTime":"19:09","endTime":"19:09","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Would it be, though, all under the umbrella of the project?","startTime":"19:09","endTime":"19:12","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Yep.","startTime":"19:13","endTime":"19:13","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"19:14","endTime":"19:15","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"19:15","endTime":"19:15","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"That makes sense.","startTime":"19:15","endTime":"19:16","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"19:16","endTime":"19:16","speaker_name":"Debbie Herbert","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Yep.","startTime":"19:16","endTime":"19:16","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So it's really identifying which one.","startTime":"19:16","endTime":"19:17","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Did we accept this is the one that gets officially tied to it?","startTime":"19:17","endTime":"19:21","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"19:21","endTime":"19:22","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"19:22","endTime":"19:23","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"19:24","endTime":"19:24","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"19:25","endTime":"19:26","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"But I. I don't think we have.","startTime":"19:26","endTime":"19:27","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"To have like a rule around who approves.","startTime":"19:27","endTime":"19:29","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Got it.","startTime":"19:31","endTime":"19:31","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"That's great.","startTime":"19:32","endTime":"19:32","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"And the acceptance.","startTime":"19:32","endTime":"19:34","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So that works out well.","startTime":"19:34","endTime":"19:35","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And there's really no official rejection or send back information, which is great.","startTime":"19:35","endTime":"19:39","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We got that.","startTime":"19:39","endTime":"19:40","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"All right.","startTime":"19:41","endTime":"19:41","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"In one of our conversations, we talked.","startTime":"19:42","endTime":"19:43","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"About.","startTime":"19:43","endTime":"19:44","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"Understanding what labor quotes are out there.","startTime":"19:45","endTime":"19:48","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And I think we talked about having a dashboard, putting together a dashboard for those labor quotes.","startTime":"19:48","endTime":"19:53","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I just had a note here to confirm that we're all on the same page with that.","startTime":"19:54","endTime":"19:57","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We have some fields that we would put on there.","startTime":"19:57","endTime":"19:59","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But does that sound right?","startTime":"19:59","endTime