now if you're typically doing it.","startTime":"26:12","endTime":"26:14","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Definitely want to do that.","startTime":"26:14","endTime":"26:15","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, perfect.","startTime":"26:15","endTime":"26:16","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Great.","startTime":"26:16","endTime":"26:17","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And right now our.","startTime":"26:19","endTime":"26:20","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, because everything is just.","startTime":"26:20","endTime":"26:21","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"It's a standalone.","startTime":"26:21","endTime":"26:22","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So.","startTime":"26:22","endTime":"26:23","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, design request is a Google worksheet PM request is a Google worksheet.","startTime":"26:23","endTime":"26:27","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Like everything is a Google worksheet that then dumps into a separate.","startTime":"26:27","endTime":"26:30","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So Kimmy and I did a vlookup segment of seven different Google worksheets.","startTime":"26:31","endTime":"26:37","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"That kind of gives us a very slow pulse on what's happening in the world.","startTime":"26:37","endTime":"26:41","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Thanks.","startTime":"26:42","endTime":"26:43","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"26:43","endTime":"26:43","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"I didn't even know Google Sheets had Vlookups yet.","startTime":"26:45","endTime":"26:47","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":